The always outspoken and "controversial" Gavin McInnes joins the Anthony Cumia Network - with new shows twice a week. In addition to co-founding VICE, the author, actor, musician, podcast host, and political pundit is at the forefront of the modern "anti-PC" movement and a perfect match for the cutting edge and newly emerging ACN.

Guests: J Penry, Jayson Green, Mike David, Mike Ward, Milo Yiannopoulos

Episode 47 - Gavin is joined again by Mike Ward. They talk about Poutine and Gavin's Indian necklace. Jayson Green and J Penry are back to talk about everything from toe rings to music. Milo talks about progressive left exclusions and the silent majority, and Red Bar Radio Show host Mike David talks about Jamie Kilstien.
